</div><a name="tip-133989"></a>
							<div class="KonaBody">
								<div class="tip" tipid="133989" comments="1" rating="10">
									<h2><a href="http://cooking.lifetips.com/tip/133989/cooking-tips/baking-tips/test-for-baking-powder.html" title="Test for Baking Powder">Test for Baking Powder</a></h2>
									<p>If you're unsure about the freshness of your baking powder try this test. Put one teaspoon in 1/3 cup of water. If the water does not fizz toss the baking powder. It's too old.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
