									<h2><a href="http://cooking.lifetips.com/tip/88111/cooking-tips/cooking-tips/stop-fried-foods-from-sticking.html" title="Stop fried foods from sticking">Stop fried foods from sticking</a></h2>
									<p>To keep your breaded, fried foods from sticking to the pan, do NOT preheat the pan and oil before adding the meat. Start with a cool pan and your breading will stay on the meat. Also look for top quality non stick cookware!</p>
